ReflectiveClone This non-instantiable non-extendible class provides a static clone() method suitable for cloning an instance of a class satisfying the following constraints: no-arg constructor is available (not necessarily public) neither the class nor any of its superclasses have any final fields neither the class nor any of its superclasses have any inner classes This class requires sufficient security privileges to work.
